summary: I’ve just realized that most of you have probably never seen either of my two lovely daughters. Hence, I’ve decided to make your...
body:
I’ve just realized that most of you have probably never seen either of my two lovely daughters. Hence, I’ve decided to make your day with a “selfie” I took during battle training about a couple of months ago. 

As you can see, that’s me in the center. Gamora is the lovely young lady on the right doing the flying jump kick, and Nebula is the one on the left holding the knife. Somehow I think I managed to get Ronan and Korath in the background as well.

Now, I don’t mean to be one of those parents who say “my kids could beat up your kids” but Gamora is widely known as the most deadly woman in the galaxy. And if you’ve ever seen her swordsmanship, you’d know that’s no exaggeration– she wields that weapon as though it were a song and she the composer. Even Nebula is considered to be a galaxy-class killer, and although she’s never bested her sister in combat, she fights with such grace.

Hmm. Well, I suppose I really did mean to be one of those parents. 

Oh well.

There are worse things to be, don’t you think?
